graph TB
    subgraph TrainingOperator["Training Operator (KFTO)"]
        direction TB
        Main[training-operator<br/>Go Operator]
        CertCtrl[cert-controller<br/>TLS cert rotation]

        subgraph Controllers["Job Controllers"]
            PyTorchCtrl[pytorchjob-controller]
            TFCtrl[tfjob-controller]
            XGBoostCtrl[xgboostjob-controller]
            MPICtrl[mpijob-controller]
            PaddleCtrl[paddlejob-controller]
            JAXCtrl[jaxjob-controller]
        end

        Webhook[ValidatingWebhookConfiguration<br/>Port 9443/TCP TLS]

        Main --> Controllers
        Main --> Webhook
        Main --> CertCtrl
        CertCtrl -->|manages TLS certs| Webhook
    end

    %% CRDs
    User[User / Client] -->|creates| PyTorchJobCR[PyTorchJob CR]
    User -->|creates| TFJobCR[TFJob CR]
    User -->|creates| XGBoostJobCR[XGBoostJob CR]
    User -->|creates| MPIJobCR[MPIJob CR]
    User -->|creates| PaddleJobCR[PaddleJob CR]
    User -->|creates| JAXJobCR[JAXJob CR]

    %% CR to Controller mappings
    PyTorchJobCR -->|watched by| PyTorchCtrl
    TFJobCR -->|watched by| TFCtrl
    XGBoostJobCR -->|watched by| XGBoostCtrl
    MPIJobCR -->|watched by| MPICtrl
    PaddleJobCR -->|watched by| PaddleCtrl
    JAXJobCR -->|watched by| JAXCtrl

    %% Resources created by controllers
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Pods[Pods]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Services[Headless Services]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| NetPol[NetworkPolicies]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| HPA[HPA<br/>optional elastic]

    TFCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    XGBoostCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    MPICtrl -->|creates| Pods
    PaddleCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    JAXCtrl -->|creates| Pods

    %% External dependencies
    Main -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Main -.->|optional| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>PodGroups]
    Main -.->|optional| SchedPlugins[scheduler-plugins<br/>PodGroups]
    Main -.->|optional| Kueue[Kueue<br/>MultiKueue]

    %% Deployment
    RhodsOp[rhods-operator] -->|deploys via kustomize| Main

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>openshift-monitoring] -->|scrapes :8080| Main

